itunes:title: Listen to this if you need a tough love reminder
title: Listen to this if you need a tough love reminder
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
description:
This was quite the emotional podcast for me but I needed it. This is for anyone who needs a reminder to get back to working on themselves. To get up off the couch, to stop mindlessly scrolling and to get back to who they are
